comments: Curry (PHI) brings his left hand toward Anthony's (ORL) right side and releases away without applying any force as Anthony fades away during the jump shot attempt.
Embiid (PHI) firms up in his screening position in Harris' (ORL) path and absorbs the contact.
Embiid (PHI) jumps alongside Anthony's (ORL) path and he lightly brushes Anthony's extended off-arm before cleanly blocking the shot attempt.
Bamba (ORL) brings his hand toward Harris' (PHI) front and marginal contact occurs as Harris retrieves the rebound.
Embiid (PHI) and Bamba (ORL) engage and disengage with one another in the lane.
Carter Jr. (ORL) extends his hands into Curry's (PHI) front and initiates contact that alters Curry's body trajectory during the driving shot attempt.
Niang (PHI) and Anthony (ORL) engage and disengage with one another during the inbound.
Embiid (PHI) engages and disengages with Bamba (ORL) as Bamba sets the pick.
Embiid (PHI) brings his left hand toward Ross' (ORL) front and marginal contact occurs as Ross dribbles toward the sideline.
Korkmaz (PHI) briefly has his arm around Ross' (ORL) midsection and quickly slides it off during the inbound.
The ball touches Embiid's (PHI) leg last before it goes out of bounds.
Embiid (PHI) turns to begin rolling out of his screening position and his right forearm releases away from Anthony's (ORL) side without applying any force.
Anthony (ORL) jumps forward and delivers contact to Korkmaz's (PHI) left side along the sideline.
Bamba (ORL) firms up in his screening position in Korkmaz's (PHI) path and he absorbs the marginal body contact during the screen.
Bamba (ORL) and Harris (PHI) come together at the same spot in the lane and marginal body contact occurs as they each attempt to establish rebounding position.
Correctly called 24 second violation on PHI.
